# Day 958

![Smoking On That Make America Great Again Pack](https://miro.medium.com/1*uDbOZVz_Webcmq8V-hzEyA.png)

We will be finding out who the next President of the United States is very soon. I pray it is the individual who will bring about less war, who will help fix the money, who will pardon Ross, and who will do everything in their power to help America and the world thrive.

I just said a prayer, amen.

11/4/24

Conor Jay Chepenik
